com.matrixone.apps.domain.util
Class Request

java.lang.Object
  com.matrixone.apps.domain.util.Request
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Request
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The Request class provides tools for accessing information about the Request object. This class is intended for use within jsp pages. Regardless of how the jsp page is submitted, this class provides functions to retrieve the data in a proper way accounting for multi-byte code, multi-part requests, etc. 1. Call one of the processForm methods.

Version:
AEF 9.1.0.0 - Copyright (c) 2001, MatrixOne, Inc.
